    "It can also monitor risks and provide compliance reports.",
    "In addition, AI technology can help deliver personalised services to customers, thereby optimising their experience.",
    "AI technology can provide customised financial product recommendations, intelligent investment advice and financial planning for customer credit risk by analysing customer data and behavioural patterns, including personal information, credit history, financial status, career background and social networking behaviour.AI is poised to revolutionize the financial industry, particularly within the credit and auto loan sector, by introducing unprecedented efficiency, accuracy, and customer personalization.",
